00:21:37.520 --> 00:21:39.520
or a Mae Sue Cleansing Ceremony.

00:21:39.720 --> 00:21:41.680
The doll’s left at a crossroads.

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:42.960
Yes, Monk.

00:21:42.960 --> 00:21:44.680
Grandmaster Monk once told me

00:21:44.680 --> 00:21:46.960
I went through that ritual myself as a kid.

00:21:46.960 --> 00:21:48.760
Villagers believe that

00:21:48.760 --> 00:21:51.320
the clay doll represents that child.

00:21:51.600 --> 00:21:54.040
Once the spirit Mae Sue takes the doll,

00:21:54.040 --> 00:21:55.840
it won’t harm the child again.

00:21:55.960 --> 00:21:58.920
These rituals vary from place to place.

00:21:59.360 --> 00:22:01.480
