00:22:47.880 --> 00:22:49.640
wrapped in a cloth talisman,

00:22:50.280 --> 00:22:51.800
a ghost-summoning talisman,

00:22:53.160 --> 00:22:55.240
and buried underground.

00:22:58.360 --> 00:23:00.440
I think someone cursed them.

00:23:03.600 --> 00:23:06.520
When that happens, their life force weakens.

00:23:07.080 --> 00:23:09.080
And spirits can harm them.

00:23:09.480 --> 00:23:11.360
All that... just from one doll?

