00:23:28.280 --> 00:23:30.280
dolls like these,

00:23:30.280 --> 00:23:32.160
no temple would ever give them out.

00:23:32.160 --> 00:23:34.000
Only from...

00:23:36.120 --> 00:23:37.640
a shaman’s house,

00:23:37.680 --> 00:23:39.440
or a medium’s shrine.

00:23:44.320 --> 00:23:46.000
Not like I have many options.

00:23:46.800 --> 00:23:48.280
